🔸 1. Prompt Chaining

Break complex tasks into multiple prompts.

🔸 2. Self-Consistency

Generate multiple outputs and select the best.

🔸 3. ReAct (Reason + Act)

Combines reasoning with actions (used in agents).

🔸 4. Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
Combines external data with LLM
Improves factual accuracy


❌ Common Mistakes
Vague instructions
No context provided
Overly long prompts
Ignoring output format
Not iterating on prompts


✅ Best Practices
Be specific and explicit
Use structured formats (bullets, JSON)
Define output format clearly
Iterate and refine prompts
Test with multiple inputs


